    "As the degree of discreteness and nonequilibrium increases, the complexity of system behavior sharply increases, which poses challenges for the description and control of corresponding flow behavior.",
    "Our understanding of fluid behavior has two progression modes: one is the macroscopic cognitive progression mode centered on conserved quantities, and the other is the microscopic cognitive progression mode centered on molecular dynamics.",
